1. *Razumem* ga, ali ne mogu da mu pomognem. (I understand him, but I can't help him.)
2. *Razumem* te, ali ne mogu da ti pomognem. (I understand you, but I can't help you.)
3. On me *razume*. (He understands me.)
4. Da li me *razume≈°*? (Do you understand me?) 
5. Ona me *razume*. (She understands me.)
6. Ne *razumem*. (I don't understand.) 
7. Oni me *razumeju*. (They understand me.)